The paper discusses the use of robots in extreme environments, which is a common topic in the robotics community (cs.RO). The paper also focuses on the need for operational autonomy and safety, which are key concerns in artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and control systems (cs.SY). The paper also discusses the use of probabilistic model checking, which is a common technique in software engineering (cs.SE) and computer security (cs.CR).
